OL,3,CHome Office 'wasted' #15m of
OL,4,Ctaxpayers' cash on asbestos-filled
OL,5,Cmigrant camp
OL,7,FThe Home Office spent #15 million
OL,8,Fbuying a derelict prison contaminated
OL,9,Fwith asbestos amid political pressure
OL,10,Fto stop housing migrants in hotels,
OL,11,Faccording to Whitehall's spending
OL,12,Fwatchdog.
OL,14,FThe government department cut corners
OL,15,Fand paid more than it needed to in its
OL,16,Fhaste to acquire the Northeye site in
OL,17,FBexhill-on-Sea, East Sussex, but this
OL,18,Fwas "ultimately deemed unfit for its
OL,19,Fintended purpose due to
OL,20,Fcontamination", the National Audit
OL,21,FOffice (NAO) said.
