OL,5,Cmigrant camp
OL,7,FThe sale came after then-prime
OL,8,Fminister Rishi Sunak vowed on December
OL,9,F13 2022 to stop housing asylum seekers
OL,10,Fin hotels and find accommodation in
OL,11,Fdisused holiday parks, former student
OL,12,Fhalls and surplus military sites
OL,13,Finstead, telling the Commons, "unless
OL,14,Fwe act now, and decisively, this will
OL,15,Fonly get worse".
OL,17,FThe statement in Parliament "generated
OL,18,Fsignificant pressure within the Home
OL,19,FOffice to identify and secure sites
OL,20,Ffor asylum accommodation at pace", the
OL,21,Freport said.
