OL,7,FThat same month the Home Office
OL,8,F"decided to acquire the Northeye site
OL,9,Fthrough purchasing it from the vendors
OL,10,Frather than lease the site" as
OL,11,Finitially planned, the NAO found.
OL,13,FBy January 16 2023 the Home Office had
OL,14,Finstructed property advisers to make
OL,15,Fan offer to the Northeye site vendors
OL,16,Fbased on completion within six weeks.
