OL,7,FThe site was one of four "acquired by
OL,8,Fthe Home Office under the direction of
OL,9,Fthe small ministerial group" and by
OL,10,FJanuary 19 2023 the group agreed to
OL,11,Fprioritise the Northeye site,
OL,12,Faccording to the report.
OL,14,FThe NAO said the group, set up in
OL,15,FNovember 2022, was made up of
OL,16,F"ministers and officials from across
OL,17,FWhitehall, including the minister for
OL,18,Fimmigration, and was chaired by the
OL,19,FChancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster".
