OL,7,FThese positions were at the time held
OL,8,Fby Robert Jenrick ` now the shadow
OL,9,Fjustice secretary after his failed bid
OL,10,Fto become Tory leader ` and Oliver
OL,11,FDowden, who was later appointed deputy
OL,12,Fprime minister.
OL,14,FIn February 2023 planning checks
OL,15,Frevealed "high risk" contamination
OL,16,Facross the site and a further review
OL,17,Fconcluded the "primary contamination
OL,18,Frisk was from asbestos-containing
OL,19,Fmaterials in existing buildings and
OL,20,Fcontaminated ground".
