OL,7,FIn July this year the Home Office said
OL,8,Fno decision had been made on the use
OL,9,Fof the site and it would "consider its
OL,10,Fstrategy and broader requirements
OL,11,Fbefore taking a view on the future use
OL,12,Fof it".
OL,14,FWhile the site "may yet fulfil a need
OL,15,Fthe Home Office has, it remains to be
OL,16,Fseen whether the acquisition of the
OL,17,FNortheye site results in benefits that
OL,18,Fjustify its cost", the NAO added.
