OL,7,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,8,Fof the Commons Public Accounts
OL,9,FCommittee, said: "Once again, rushed
OL,10,Fand misjudged decision-making has
OL,11,Fresulted in the Home Office overpaying
OL,12,Ffor an asylum accommodation site that
OL,13,Fis not fit for purpose.
OL,15,F"I am concerned that the Home Office
OL,16,Fdeviated from standard practice,
OL,17,Foverlooked warnings about the
OL,18,Fcondition of the site and lacked
OL,19,Fexpertise to properly oversee the
OL,20,Fpurchase of Northeye.
