OL,7,F"The Public Accounts Committee has
OL,8,Fpreviously warned about the risks to
OL,9,Ftaxpayer money when departments forego
OL,10,Fdue diligence in making decisions at
OL,11,Fpace.
OL,13,F"My committee will be following up on
OL,14,Fthis issue to ensure that continuous
OL,15,Fmistakes are not made and public money
OL,16,Fis not wasted in future acquisitions."
