OL,7,FLou Calvey, director of charity Asylum
OL,8,FMatters, which campaigns for migrants
OL,9,Fto be housed in communities instead of
OL,10,Fcamps, said more than #15 million of
OL,11,Fpublic money was "thrown away on a
OL,12,Fcontaminated and dangerous site that
OL,13,Fshould never have been under
OL,14,Fconsideration".
OL,16,FShe accused the previous government of
OL,17,F"ignoring warnings so it could indulge
OL,18,Fin waste and carelessness, putting
OL,19,Fcruel ideology above everything else `
OL,20,Fincluding value for the taxpayer".
